    <item>
      <title>随着日本贸易繁荣，大和的利润增加了一倍多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/daiwa-s-profit-more-than-doubles-as-trading-booms-in-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大和证券集团 (Daiwa Securities Group Inc.) 的季度利润增长了一倍以上，这得益于日本基准股票指数在当季创下历史新高，日本第二大券商的交易量激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/daiwa-s-profit-more-than-doubles-as-trading-booms-in-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:13:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
