      <title>随着电动汽车需求疲软，现代汽车将在混合动力汽车上投入更多资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/hyundai-motor-profit-beats-estimates-on-weaker-korean-won</link>
